            </div>

            <!-- Panduan Testing Postman -->
            <div class="doc-section" id="postman">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <span class="section-icon">üìÆ</span>
                    <span>Panduan Testing dengan Postman</span>
                </div>
                
                <p>Postman adalah tools profesional untuk testing API. Berikut panduan lengkap menggunakan <strong>raw JSON body</strong>.</p>

                <!-- Register -->
                <div class="endpoint-card">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="method-badge method-post">POST</span>
                        Test 1: Register User Baru
                    </h3>
                    <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>/api/auth/register</code></p>
                    <p><strong>Kegunaan:</strong> Membuat akun user baru untuk mendapatkan akses ke API</p>

                    <h4>üìã Langkah di Postman:</h4>
                    <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                        <li>Buka Postman</li>
                        <li>Buat request baru: Method <strong>POST</strong></li>
                        <li>URL: <code>http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register</code></li>
                        <li>Tab <strong>Body</strong> ‚Üí Pilih <strong>raw</strong> ‚Üí Dropdown pilih <strong>JSON</strong></li>
                        <li>Masukkan JSON body:</li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="code-block">{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123",
  "role": "user"
}</div>

                    <h4>6. Klik <strong>Send</strong></h4>
                    <h4>Response (201 Created):</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Registrasi berhasil! Silakan login",
  "data": {
    "userId": 5,
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "role": "user"
  }
}</div>

                    <div class="warning-box">
                        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Validasi:</strong>
                        <ul style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                            <li>Semua field wajib diisi</li>
                            <li>Password minimal 6 karakter</li>
                            <li>Password harus sama dengan confirmPassword</li>
                            <li>Email harus unik (belum terdaftar)</li>
                            <li>Role: <code>user</code> atau <code>admin</code></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Login -->
                <div class="endpoint-card">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="method-badge method-post">POST</span>
                        Test 2: Login & Dapat API Key
                    </h3>
                    <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>/api/auth/login</code></p>
                    <p><strong>Kegunaan:</strong> Login dan langsung mendapatkan API Key untuk akses data konser</p>

                    <h4>üìã Langkah di Postman:</h4>
                    <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                        <li>Buat request baru: Method <strong>POST</strong></li>
                        <li>URL: <code>http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login</code></li>
                        <li>Tab <strong>Body</strong> ‚Üí Pilih <strong>raw</strong> ‚Üí <strong>JSON</strong></li>
                        <li>Masukkan JSON body:</li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="code-block">{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}</div>

                    <h4>5. Klik <strong>Send</strong></h4>
                    <h4>Response (200 OK):</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Login berhasil",
  "data": {
    "userId": 5,
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "role": "user",
    "apiKey": "koncr_abc123xyz456"  ‚Üê COPY API KEY INI!
  }
}</div>

                    <div class="info-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4fc79 0%, #96e6a1 100%); border-left-color: #38ef7d;">
                        <strong>‚úÖ Penting:</strong> Response login akan memberikan <strong>API Key</strong>. 
                        <strong>Copy API Key</strong> tersebut (contoh: <code>koncr_abc123xyz456</code>). 
                        API Key ini akan digunakan untuk semua request selanjutnya!
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Get Concerts -->
                <div class="endpoint-card">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="method-badge method-get">GET</span>
                        Test 3: Melihat Semua Data Konser
                    </h3>
                    <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>/api/concerts</code></p>
                    <p><strong>Kegunaan:</strong> Mendapatkan daftar semua konser dengan validasi API Key</p>

                    <h4>üìã Langkah di Postman:</h4>
                    <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                        <li>Buat request baru: Method <strong>GET</strong></li>
                        <li>URL: <code>http://localhost:3000/api/concerts</code></li>
                        <li>Tab <strong>Headers</strong> ‚Üí Klik "Add"</li>
                        <li>Tambahkan header:
                            <div class="code-block" style="margin: 10px 0;">Key: X-API-Key
Value: koncr_abc123xyz456  (paste API Key dari login)</div>
                        </li>
                        <li>Klik <strong>Send</strong></li>
                    </ol>

                    <h4>Response (200 OK):</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Rock Festival 2026",
      "artist": "The Rockers",
      "genre": "rock",
      "date": "2026-03-15",
      "time": "19:00",
      "location": "Jakarta Stadium",
      "price": 500000,
      "description": "Festival rock terbesar",
      "image_url": "/uploads/concerts/rock.jpg",
      "music_url": "/uploads/music/rock-anthem.mp3"
    },
    ...
  ]
}</div>

                    <div class="warning-box">
                        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Jika Error 401 "API key tidak valid":</strong>
                        <ol style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                            <li>Pastikan header <code>X-API-Key</code> diketik dengan benar (case sensitive)</li>
                            <li>Pastikan API Key yang di-paste benar (tidak ada spasi extra)</li>
                            <li>Coba login ulang dan copy API Key baru</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Filter & Search -->
                <div class="endpoint-card">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="method-badge method-get">GET</span>
                        Test 4: Filter & Search Konser
                    </h3>
                    
                    <h4>Filter by Genre:</h4>
                    <p>URL: <code>http://localhost:3000/api/concerts?genre=rock</code></p>
                    <p>Headers: <code>X-API-Key: your-api-key</code></p>
                    <p>Genre valid: <code>rock</code>, <code>pop</code>, <code>jazz</code>, <code>electronic</code></p>

                    <h4>Search by Keyword:</h4>
                    <p>URL: <code>http://localhost:3000/api/concerts?search=Festival</code></p>
                    <p>Akan mencari di field <code>name</code> dan <code>artist</code></p>

                    <h4>Kombinasi Filter + Search:</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">http://localhost:3000/api/concerts?genre=rock&search=Jakarta</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Get by ID -->
                <div class="endpoint-card">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="method-badge method-get">GET</span>
                        Test 5: Melihat Detail Konser Spesifik
                    </h3>
                    <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>/api/concerts/:id</code></p>

                    <h4>üìã Langkah di Postman:</h4>
                    <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                        <li>Method: <strong>GET</strong></li>
                        <li>URL: <code>http://localhost:3000/api/concerts/1</code> (ganti 1 dengan ID yang diinginkan)</li>
                        <li>Tab <strong>Headers</strong> ‚Üí Add: <code>X-API-Key: your-api-key</code></li>
                        <li>Klik <strong>Send</strong></li>
                    </ol>

                    <h4>Response (200 OK):</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Rock Festival 2026",
    "artist": "The Rockers",
    ...
  }
}</div>

                    <h4>Response Error (404 Not Found):</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">{
  "success": false,
  "error": "Konser tidak ditemukan"
}</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Add Concert -->
                <div class="endpoint-card">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="method-badge method-post">POST</span>
                        Test 6: Menambah Konser Baru (Admin Only)
                    </h3>
                    <p><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code>/api/concerts</code> <span style="background: #ff6b6b; color: white; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.8em;">ADMIN ONLY</span></p>
                    <p><strong>Kegunaan:</strong> Admin dapat menambah konser baru via API</p>

                    <h4>üìã Langkah di Postman:</h4>
                    <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
                        <li>Pastikan Anda sudah register dengan <code>role: "admin"</code></li>
                        <li>Login dan copy API Key admin</li>
                        <li>Buat request baru: Method <strong>POST</strong></li>
                        <li>URL: <code>http://localhost:3000/api/concerts</code></li>
                        <li>Tab <strong>Headers</strong> ‚Üí Add: <code>X-API-Key: admin-api-key</code></li>
                        <li>Tab <strong>Body</strong> ‚Üí Pilih <strong>raw</strong> ‚Üí <strong>JSON</strong></li>
                        <li>Masukkan JSON body:</li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="code-block">{
  "name": "Rock Festival 2026",
  "artist": "The Rockers",
  "genre": "rock",
  "date": "2026-03-15",
  "time": "19:00",
  "location": "Jakarta Stadium",
  "price": 500000,
  "description": "Festival rock terbesar tahun ini",
  "image_url": "/uploads/concerts/rock-festival.jpg",
  "music_url": "/uploads/music/rock-anthem.mp3"
}</div>

                    <h4>8. Klik <strong>Send</strong></h4>
                    <h4>Response (201 Created):</h4>
                    <div class="code-block">{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Konser berhasil ditambahkan",
  "data": {
    "id": 15,
    "name": "Rock Festival 2026",
    "artist": "The Rockers",
    "genre": "rock",
    "date": "2026-03-15",
    "time": "19:00",
    "location": "Jakarta Stadium",
    "price": 500000,
    "description": "Festival rock terbesar tahun ini",
    "image_url": "/uploads/concerts/rock-festival.jpg",
    "music_url": "/uploads/music/rock-anthem.mp3",
    "created_at": "2026-01-11T10:00:00.000Z"
  }
}</div>

                    <h4>üìù Field Description:</h4>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">name</span>
                        <span class="badge-required">Required</span>
                        <span>Judul konser (contoh: Rock Festival 2026)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">artist</span>
                        <span class="badge-required">Required</span>
                        <span>Nama artist/penyanyi</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">genre</span>
                        <span class="badge-required">Required</span>
                        <span>Nilai valid: <code>rock</code>, <code>pop</code>, <code>jazz</code>, <code>electronic</code></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">date</span>
                        <span class="badge-required">Required</span>
                        <span>Format: <code>YYYY-MM-DD</code> (contoh: 2026-03-15)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">time</span>
                        <span class="badge-required">Required</span>
                        <span>Format: <code>HH:MM</code> (contoh: 19:00, 20:30)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">location</span>
                        <span class="badge-required">Required</span>
                        <span>Lokasi konser (contoh: Jakarta Stadium)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">price</span>
                        <span class="badge-required">Required</span>
                        <span>Tipe: <code>number</code> - Harga tiket dalam Rupiah (contoh: 500000)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">description</span>
                        <span class="badge-optional">Optional</span>
                        <span>Deskripsi konser</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">image_url</span>
                        <span class="badge-optional">Optional</span>
                        <span>Path gambar konser (format: JPG, PNG, GIF - max 5MB)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-row">
                        <span class="param-name">music_url</span>
                        <span class="badge-optional">Optional</span>
                        <span>Path musik MP3 (format: MP3 - max 20MB)</span>
